server.commands

Class CommandResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • server.commands.CommandResponse

  • public class CommandResponse
extends java.lang.Object
    Holds the response that should be returned to the Client. This will be returned to the Facade which will then return it to the Handlers which will convert it to an HttpExchange object.
